name: 1000 Boudoir Glam shot Poses
description:
1000 Boudoir Glam shot Poses

V1 Used the new "BODY25" 25 point Skeleton extraction methods which is a more advanced and accurate method, but the skeletons used in openpose for Automatic1111 is based of "COCO" 18 point skeletons, I didn't know this so I re-extracted everything. My extractions works better now.

I was experimenting with Openpose and extracted myself a few Poses from a pdf I found on Boudoir and Glam shots, thought it turned out not too bad so I'm sharing it with you guys.

I saw some poses with included hands as depth, if anyone has some feedback how to get that working I will definitely update this collection.

I have more reference images that I will add as soon as I have processed the datasets. This dataset's original images can be found here:

Boudoir and Glam Dataset used
